OL,7,Fcurrent address would not be a
OL,8,Fsuitable bail address but he argued
OL,9,Fthat with the investigation and and
OL,10,Fforensic testing "going to take a very
OL,11,Flong time," the defendant could be
OL,12,Ffreed on bail with conditions.
